ias.title: You're logged in as %s.
ias.loginGui.add.button.tooltip: By pressing this button you'll add an offline account. You won't be able to join servers with that account. Use 'Microsoft' button to add a normal account.
ias.loginGui.edit.button.tooltip: By pressing this button you'll make this account offline. You won't be able to join servers with that account. Use 'Microsoft' button to use a normal account.
ias.deleteGui.title: Are you sure you want to delete this account?
ias.configGui.title: In-Game Account Switcher Config
modmenu.descriptionTranslation.ias: Allows you to change which account you are signed in to in-game without restarting Minecraft.
modmenu.summaryTranslation.ias: Allows you to change your account in-game.
